lead_paragraph: Virat Kohli's elegant unbeaten 90 and some crafty bowling by their spinners secured India's comprehensive 37-run victory over Australia in the first Twenty20 International at the Adelaide Oval on Tuesday.

headline.print_headline: Kohli, Spinners Secure India's T20 Win Against Australia
